Author: AurumService
Title: [ANN][AURUM] AURUM.SERVICES - Auction and Marketplace on Blockchain
Body: What can we improve worldwide?  It is unsafe to buy used jewelry and watches online because their origin and quality are unknown; the characteristics declared by the seller are not guaranteed by anyone.  There is no possibility to sell jewelry and watches online for a satisfactory price because there is no way to confirm their authenticity and quality.  When buying jewellery and watches abroad, the buyer may encounter difficulties with payment, taxes and delivery  In most shopping malls in the world there are no services for the repair of jewelry and watches with high quality standards  https://preview.ibb.co/mSvUqJ/1.jpg

Author: AurumService
Title: [ANN][AURUM] AURUM.SERVICES - Auction and Marketplace on Blockchain
Body: Dear community!  Based on our work experience, communication with market professionals and  expert judgment, we estimate the secondary watch market to take up 35% of the primary sales volume.  After our project enters the market, additional growth of this segment is expected. About 40% of watches are expected to be resold at an average discount of 50%. Based on these numbers, we assume that the world resale market volume reached $ 11.4 billion in 2017.  https://preview.ibb.co/mhc4tJ/analysis_market_2_eng.png

Author: AurumService
Title: [ANN][AURUM] AURUM.SERVICES - Auction and Marketplace on Blockchain
Body: Dear community!  The company has a long-term experience on the market of the Russian Federation. The Russian market tendencies correspond to the ones of the world market.  The Russian market sales volume amounted to $ 132 million in 2017, thus continuing the trend of a gradual increase in sales. The expected volume of used watch resale in Russia should reach $145 million by 2022.  https://preview.ibb.co/kc24tJ/analysis_market_3_eng.png

Author: AurumService
Title: [ANN][AURUM] AURUM.SERVICES - Auction and Marketplace on Blockchain
Body: Dear community!  THE MARKETPLACE AND AUCTION ALSO WORK AS STOCK EXCHANGE  To participate in auction, the buyer must use any of the TOP-10 cryptocurrencies. In the future the list of acceptable currencies will expand. The user must transfer currency to his personal account, where the currency is stored in AURUM purse on the domestic exchange, in the form of input currency or any other form, chosen by the user.  The user may exchange his tokens for Aurum tokens and vice-versa, at any time. Anyone can buy or sell tokens at Aurum exchange. Users can buy tokens from each other. There will be no commission during the first year. After the first year the commission will be kept to a minimum. The commission is used to pay for delegate services of Graphene system. Pay will be issued from a specially created reserve fund.  https://preview.ibb.co/h2Edv8/marketplace_1_eng.png

Author: AurumService
Title: [ANN][AURUM] AURUM.SERVICES - Auction and Marketplace on Blockchain
Body: THE MARKETPLACE AND AUCTION ALSO WORK AS STOCK EXCHANGE  At marketplace, the sale price is fixed. The item is sold to the first buyer, who is ready to pay the price. At auction, the item is sold to the buyer, who bids the highest amount within the auction timeframe. If the seller decides to sell his item faster than the listed timeframe, he can choose to sell it to the highest bidder at that moment.  Once the highest bid offer is accepted, the money is withdrawn from the buyer's account. The sale time limit cannot exceed 1 year from the time the lot was placed.  https://preview.ibb.co/gF5who/marketplace_2_eng.png
